text: Ondra may refer to: *Adam Ondra (born 1993), Czech rock climber *Anny Ondra (1903–1987), Czech film actress *Jiří Ondra (born 1957), Czech soccer player *Óndra Łysohorsky (1905-1989), Czech poet *Tesla ONDRA, home computer from 1985 developed in Elstroj, produced by Tesla Liberec and later Tesla Blatna
title: Ondra
